754
01:14:47,370 --> 01:14:49,167
HENRY:
Shut up. We gotta think of Josie.

755
01:14:49,330 --> 01:14:51,480
Josie, Josie, Josie.

756
01:14:52,770 --> 01:14:55,364
"Josie Rinkenhauer."

757
01:15:13,690 --> 01:15:16,124
[BOYS GASPING]

758
01:15:48,450 --> 01:15:51,999
-Josie?
-That's right. Can you find Josie?

759
01:16:31,850 --> 01:16:34,523
JONESY: This is completely crazy.
-You can say that again.

760
01:16:34,690 --> 01:16:36,999
-I didn't say anything.
BEAVER: You did. I heard you.

761
01:16:37,170 --> 01:16:41,243
-You said, "This is completely crazy."
-I didn't say that.

762
01:16:42,170 --> 01:16:44,081
